local filedata = readFile(self.pinIn.filename.value)
local dtable = {}
for k,v in string.gmatch(filedata, "([^%c]+)=([^%c]+)") do
    dtable[k] = v
end
self.pinOut.output.value = dtable

local dtable = self.pinIn.input.value
local csid = tonumber(dtable["csid"])
local scount = tonumber(dtable["scount"])
self.pinOut.scount.value = scount
self.pinOut.csid.value = csid
self.pinOut.csfile.value = "nordRaceWeek/stage" .. csid
self.pinOut.lastDone.value =  dtable["stage" .. scount] ~= "-1"

local filedata = readFile(self.pinIn.filename.value)
local dtable = {}
for k,v in string.gmatch(filedata, "([^%c]+)=([^%c]+)") do
    dtable[k] = v
end
self.pinOut.output.value = dtable

local dtable = self.pinIn.input.value
self.pinOut.model.value = dtable["model"]
self.pinOut.config.value = dtable["config"]

local extensions = require("extensions")
local dtable = self.pinIn.input.value
local scount = tonumber(dtable["scount"])
local sid = tonumber(dtable["csid"])
local psplit = extensions.nrwutils.ssplit(dtable["stage" .. sid], ",")
local csms = tonumber(psplit[1])
local cstime = extensions.nrwutils.msToTimeTable(csms)
local toRet = ""
toRet = "Current Stage: " .. sid .. "/" .. scount .. "\n"
if csms ~= -1 then
toRet = toRet .. "Best Time: " .. extensions.nrwutils.formatTimeTable(cstime) .. "\n\n"
else
toRet = toRet .. "Best Time: No Time\n\n"
end

for i=1,scount do
psplit = extensions.nrwutils.ssplit(dtable["stage" .. i], ",")
csms = tonumber(psplit[1])
if csms ~= -1 then
cstime = extensions.nrwutils.msToTimeTable(csms)
toRet = toRet .. "Stage " .. i .. " : " .. extensions.nrwutils.formatTimeTable(cstime) .. " (" .. psplit[2] .. ")\n"
else
toRet = toRet .. "Stage " .. i .. " : No Time\n"
end
end

self.pinOut.ptext.value = toRet

local filedata = ""
local dtable = self.pinIn.current.value
local scount = tonumber(dtable["scount"])
for i=1,scount do
dtable["stage" .. i] = "-1"
end

dtable["csid"] = "1"

for k,v in pairs(dtable) do
filedata = filedata .. k .."=" .. v .. "\n"
end

writeFile("nordRaceWeek/progress", filedata)

local dtable = self.pinIn.sdata.value
local extensions = require("extensions")
local bronze = tonumber(dtable["bronze"])
local silver = tonumber(dtable["silver"])
local gold = tonumber(dtable["gold"])
local author = tonumber(dtable["author"])

local ctime = extensions.nrwutils.msToTimeTable(bronze)
local toRet = "Bronze Medal: " ..  extensions.nrwutils.formatTimeTable(ctime) .. "\n"
ctime = extensions.nrwutils.msToTimeTable(silver)
toRet = toRet .. "Silver Medal: " .. extensions.nrwutils.formatTimeTable(ctime) .. "\n"
ctime = extensions.nrwutils.msToTimeTable(gold)
toRet = toRet .. "Gold Medal: " .. extensions.nrwutils.formatTimeTable(ctime) .. "\n"


self.pinOut.stext.value = toRet

local startid = scenetree.findObject("NRWTrigger_Start"):getId()
local midid = scenetree.findObject("NRWTrigger_Mid"):getId()
local endid = scenetree.findObject("NRWTrigger_End"):getId()
local cid = self.pinIn.cid.value
local ccp = self.pinIn.ccp.value
local finished = false

local nextid = cid or startid
local nextcp = ccp or -1

if ccp == -2 then
nextid = startid 
nextcp = -1
end

if ccp == -1 and cid == startid then
nextid = midid
nextcp = 0
end

if ccp == 0 and cid == midid then
nextid = endid
nextcp = 1
end

if ccp == 1 and cid == endid then
nextid = startid
nextcp = 2
end

if ccp == 2 and cid == startid then
nextcp = 3
nextid = -1
finished=true
end



self.pinOut.nexttrig.value = nextid
self.pinOut.nextcp.value = nextcp
self.pinOut.finished.value = finished

local extensions = require("extensions")
local dtable = self.pinIn.stageData.value
local ptable = self.pinIn.progressData.value

dump(ptable)

local bronze = tonumber(dtable["bronze"])
local silver = tonumber(dtable["silver"])
local gold = tonumber(dtable["gold"])
local author = tonumber(dtable["author"])
local stageID = self.pinIn.stageID.value
local stageCount = self.pinIn.stageCount.value
local time = self.pinIn.time.value
local nextStage = stageID
local best = tonumber(extensions.nrwutils.ssplit(ptable["stage" .. stageID], ",")[1])

if best ~= -1 then
if time > best then time=best end
end

if time < author then
ptable["stage" .. stageID] = time .. ",author"
elseif time < gold then
ptable["stage" .. stageID] = time .. ",gold"
elseif time < silver then
ptable["stage" .. stageID] = time .. ",silver"
elseif time < bronze then
ptable["stage" .. stageID] = time .. ",bronze"
else 
ptable["stage" .. stageID] = time ..",none"
end

if stageID < stageCount and time < bronze then
nextStage = stageID + 1
end

ptable["csid"] = nextStage

local filedata = ""
for k,v in pairs(ptable) do
filedata = filedata .. k .. "=" .. v .. "\n"
end
writeFile("nordRaceWeek/progress", filedata)
